ce:section.ce:para:
The HPSEC with a multi-wavelength absorbance detector operating in the spectral range of 200-500 nm allowed us to get the absorbance spectra of CDs chromophoric fractions corresponding to each chromatographic peak and to compare them with the absorbance spectra of the bulk NGO-MIX and NGO (3.5-10K) samples (Fig. 3
                        a,b, Table 1
                        ).
